                      <p>79 leaves, some of which are slightly soiled and torn, especially foll.<locus>12</locus>, <locus>62</locus>, <locus>63</locus>, and <locus>73</locus>.</p>
                    </item>
                    <item>
                      <p>Several leaves are wanting after fol.<locus>1</locus>, and a single leaf after fol.<locus>26</locus>.</p>
                    </item>
